      • getNodeTypeFromStepWorkJSONString

        public String getNodeTypeFromStepWorkJSONString(String stepWorkJSONString)
        Get the node type from the StepWork data JSON string
        Parameters:
        stepWorkJSONString - the step work data JSON string
        Returns:
        the node type for the StepWork without the "Node" part of the string e.g. if a step work is for an "OpenResponseNode" the value that is returned would be "OpenResponse"
